  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/81dddd2bf9b6b337700daa17d36c666c.avif?t=1759147006\" width=384 height=100 /></span>is a 3D platformer that’s all about bringing back the magic of the early 2000s classics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll take control of a tiny mouse with a moveset built for precision - perfect for landing on the smallest points and pulling off satisfying jumps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/e4dbbffc299b93edb148efdd4b7ca8b7.poster.avif?t=1759147006\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/e4dbbffc299b93edb148efdd4b7ca8b7.webm?t=1759147006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/e4dbbffc299b93edb148efdd4b7ca8b7.mp4?t=1759147006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/6ead6172de9d7c59052c2dda3f8ad47b.poster.avif?t=1759147006\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/6ead6172de9d7c59052c2dda3f8ad47b.webm?t=1759147006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536120/extras/6ead6172de9d7c59052c2dda3f8ad47b.mp4?t=1759147006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ex